reviewText: This is a HARD workout if you use the right weight. First time I did this workout it all most took me out. I have been exercising for years and I'm in good shape. This workout is 45 mins long but there is a dread factor for me in this workout.
This workout is great - I preferred much better than her kickboxing workouts as it was easier to follow and I wouldn't get confused with the choreography.
This is a good step up from the 2nd video, trying to get through the 3rd round of exercises is a real challenge,  just what I was looking for
This workout is tough -- but excellent.  Production and music don't distract and hinder the workout.  Thanks Ilaria for a wonderful new Athletica!
